- in order to place the commands to the screen it in necessary to use refresh or wregresh (to the specific section of the window);

- refresh -> for the whole window;
- wrefresh -> only for the selected area;

- think about the window terminal as a list of layers and a containers of memory to be changed bu the commands;

- refresh -> update the standard screen (container of all contatiners);

- std screen and actual window;

 - http://www.cs.ukzn.ac.za/~hughm/os/notes/ncurses.html#using

